[I] KDE Frameworks solution for password management

[T] KDE Wallet Manager is an application to manage passwords and secrets on the
[T] KDE Plasma environment. Using the KWallet system allows a user to manage
[T] its own secrets, but also allows a user to access passwords stored by every
[T] other application that integrates with KWallet.

[U] https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/kwallet

[A] The KDE-Team
